headline: Cascade Launches New & Improved Platinum Plus to Tackle Today’s Toughest Meal Cleanups
summary: CINCINNATI, March 10, 2025--Cascade®, America’s #1 recommended dishwasher detergent brand*, is launching New & Improved Cascade Platinum Plus to address consumers’ top concerns of stuck-on food, tough grease and spotty dishes. The new product features an upgraded formula designed to remove up to 100% of food and deliver a virtually spot-free shine and dry.
